text.text: Diners say this restaurant serves up delicious milk cake, pistachio and rose petal cake, and chocolate fudge cake, and they praise the stylish and cozy atmosphere. They also highlight the friendly and attentive service, making it a great spot to relax or catch up with friends.

originalText.text: The cakes are very tempting and you have to try them once, but brace yourself for overpriced dishes here (£6 coffee and £9 teas). The pistachio and rose cake was ridiculously sweet - we left most of it. The honey cake was good. Service pretty slow.

originalText.text:
A Must-Visit Spot for Indulgent Cakes and Trendy Food

Leto Cafe is a hidden gem just a short walk from Covent Garden station. The place is vibrant, inviting, and offers a premium experience the moment you step in. The interiors are chic and elegant, with ample seating that makes it perfect for a relaxed catch-up or a solo treat.

The menu is enticing, packed with healthy yet filling options, and the cakes are simply indulgent — definitely a must-try! Drinks are just as impressive and beautifully presented. Service is quick, friendly, and engaging, adding to the overall experience.

Yes, it’s London prices, but the quality, ambience, and attention to detail make it absolutely worth it.

Highly recommended for anyone looking to enjoy a stylish cafe experience in central London.

originalText.text: I had a lovely experience at L’ETO Covent Garden. The atmosphere is cosy and beautifully decorated, and the staff were friendly and attentive throughout. I tried the Burnt Basque Cheesecake, it was rich, absolutely delicious! Perfect spot for dessert and a relaxing break in the city. Will definitely come back!

originalText.text:
If you are in London, do not miss out on trying these deserts and cakes.
We visited the Covent Garden branch and loved the hospitality, the cakes were delicious ! ( we ordered the viral milk cake, tiramisu , Dubai cheesecake ( egg free) )

We have a lot of options for egg free and vegan cakes ( making it a highlight )

The cakes are so fresh you wouldn’t stop at one for sure.
